Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 小汐?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天图书委员是你当值?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当值的日期改过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...有东西忘拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 小汐?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和好? 那个前辈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说是因为对小汐做了那么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好好个道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭女人 把风间弄得哭成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在想起和好来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么便宜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说今天放学后在图书室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直单恋她吗 好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨君 刚才说的那个前辈是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你们无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵木千津香 是二年级的图书委员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子 风间还对她特别着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来喜欢那种类型啊 那个大咪...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人喜欢的男生喜欢上风间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她恼羞成怒把风间弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为风间对她已经没什么想法了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来并非如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样单恋才痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以赶快告白不就得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做得到就不用发愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间...喜欢的是她那种可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是可爱...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间原来喜欢天然呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起把不可爱的女孩变可爱这种积极的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许选择把不呆的女孩变呆这种退化才是捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原...原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破自己过于严谨的外壳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧化蝶成为万人皆爱的天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香·蕉·的·皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不流行这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情都要从基础学起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千里之行始于足下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,iroha的i asahi的a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.77,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(iroha是日语假名的一种排列方式 最初的三个假名是いろは)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语也要从ABC开始学起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 别人说什么你都要回嘴这点最不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是可爱不可爱之前的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当麻美耶子...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都不知道你到底是故意还是天然了 美耶子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点结束吧...午休时间...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.19,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.79,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.87,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间现在在做什么呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.64,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 答对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到小纯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学在屋顶上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和莲贺同学她们一起围着一块香蕉皮...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 踩吧 快踩!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一踩就能俘获全国天然呆爱好者的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?! 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要踩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱宫君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...昨天的班委会议...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够天然够呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还有这样一个人才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟人家比比 村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小小的场面都会恼羞成怒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是做不了一流艺人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你到底想让我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学 冷...冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她天生就是个吐槽的人嘛 没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我比较期待村雨君偶尔灵光一现的犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经跑题了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存车处要换顶棚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自行车的同学明天开始把车放到体育馆后边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在想前辈吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 可以去小纯家玩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么状况?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不选前辈 而是选我吗 难道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆一个!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨君 现在正是给她看你特训成果的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆一个 快点变成天然呆!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明白了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼 眼镜呢 眼镜在哪 啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做是不是不大好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小清她 特意来替前辈传话给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈那边不去可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她已经没感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间她...说谎了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就住小纯家里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天哥哥工作忙不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人多可怕啊 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿身换的衣服 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在身边看着风间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以知道她在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才更觉得难过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在 这个瞬间 风间她...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为想看着我才在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次去你家玩的时候 不是给你弄脏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么挂心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过 小纯也摆在桌子上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 是啊 做个纪念嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我还是也摆上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊 已经过了三个月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 发生了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.72,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐小姐 晚饭想吃什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就吃红豆饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.26,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(日本有喜事的时候会吃红豆饭表示庆祝)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小汐还是那么可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把你那可爱劲儿分给纯夏一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 每次风间来你都说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.23,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐小姐 要再来一碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.56,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我已经饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不用这么客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家纯夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时要比你多吃一倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却总是只会竖着长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话分她一半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分什么啊 哥哥们不要乱讲话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 正在吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...有人来踢馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 不知天高地的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我极北流空手道 村雨天海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区踢馆 对我来说只能算饭后甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚吃完饭这样一动 肚子好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还有这样一个人才...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 然后哥哥们忽然间...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯夏小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得风间来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家里!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我比划比划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 对我来说天然呆是有点困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始觉得有点懒得想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里连发愁的工夫都没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近学校里又被那些白痴闹得昏天黑地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小~纯~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就想试一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...真是的...这丫头真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.43,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯家的浴池好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.70,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯?小纯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把我当成朋友看啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 接下来拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野江阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩笑我可不大喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 闹得你也不得安宁的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我很喜欢小纯家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是有这么多人 多开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家最多也就我和哥哥两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是 今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 还是要说前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了 我终于摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且怎么回事...这个幸福的触感...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯? 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 风间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还晕着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 害你替我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样躲着不见 前辈也不会消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来那么喜欢的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连看都不愿看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈又没做错什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自顾自地喜欢上她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又自顾自地开始讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自顾自地...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间你 没做错什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然已经喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大家都是女孩子也是没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 有人因为这个说风间的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙 我会把他揍飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道小纯一定会这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有个好朋友就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风...风间同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天没去 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过希望你能明白 我最喜欢前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为被前辈讨厌了 真的很难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈对我怎么看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢呢 还是讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风 风间同学...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经和好了啊 她们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来「只是可靠好友的小纯」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了那个大咪咪一份多余的勇气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 风间 山崎明美小姐来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来看看吗 是明美小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁啊 放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 小纯 今天有图书委员全体会议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我也留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就期末了 我家又那么乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 多不好啊要你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下 下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:50.74,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 [少年少女]


